but you had someone you loved dearly,

51
00:04:12,170 --> 00:04:13,650
what would you do?

52
00:04:13,790 --> 00:04:14,750
Shen Zheng.

53
00:04:17,550 --> 00:04:18,510
If...

54
00:04:20,100 --> 00:04:21,149
Governor, bad...

55
